     C/SPACE 5
      *****************************************************************
      ** Determine Next and Last Coupon Dates
      *****************************************************************
     C           DETDAT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Use the maturity date if the calculation date is beyond it
      *
     C           ##IDAT    IFGT MATY
     C                     Z-ADDMATY      ##IDAT
     C                     END
      *
      ** Determine the next coupon date
      *
     C                     Z-ADD##IDAT    ECD     50
     C                     EXSR ZNCD
      *
      ** Set the accrual Indicator
      *
     C           ##IDAT    IFEQ NCD
     C                     MOVEL'F'       ##ACIN  1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL'C'       ##ACIN
     C                     END
      *
      ** Determine the last coupon date (prior to the next coupon date)
      *
     C           ##ACIN    IFEQ 'F'
     C           ##FULL    ANDNE'Y'
     C                     Z-ADD##IDAT    ZZLCD
     C                     ELSE
     C           NCD       SUB  1         ZECD
     C                     EXSR ZLCD
     C                     END
      *
      ** Last coupon date
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZZLCD     LCPN
      *
      ** Last and Next Coupon Dates for Return
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZZLCD     ##LCD
     C                     Z-ADDNCD       ##NCD
     C                     ENDSR
     C**********************************************************************
     C/SPACE 5
     C**********************************************************************
      ** Interest Calculation
     C**********************************************************************
     C           INTCAL    BEGSR
     C*
     C** SET GREATER THAN LIMITS ON LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           ##BPSK    SETGTBKPOSDF
     C*
     C** READ PREVIOUS EQUAL FROM LF/BKPOSDF
     C*
     C           ##BPSP    REDPEBKPOSDF                  91
     C*
     C** SET THE NOMINAL
     C*
     C           *IN91     IFEQ '0'
     C           NPSN      SUB  ECNP      ZAMT
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD0         ZAMT
     C                     END
     C*
     C** SET THE FIELDS FOR ZRATE
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDCPDP      ZPPCP
     C                     Z-ADDSFPP      ZSFPP
     C                     MOVE PPDI      ZPPDI
     C                     Z-ADDCPNR      ZCPNR
     C                     Z-ADDCFCT      ZCFCT
     C                     MOVE PROT      ZPROT
     C*
     C** ACCESS LF/SECED  USING A KEY OF SECURITY, LAST COUPON DATE
     C** AND EVENT TYPE EQUAL TO 'CP'
     C*
     C                     MOVEL'CP'      ##TYP
     C           ##SEVK    CHAINSECED                91
     C*
     C** IF A LAST COUPON DATE EVENT IS READ ABOVE,
     C** THEN SET THE FIELDS USED BY ZRATE
     C*
     C           *IN91     IFEQ '0'
     C                     Z-ADDSNCR      ZCPNR
     C                     Z-ADDSNCF      ZCFCT
     C                     Z-ADDSNCP      ZPPCP
     C                     END
     C*
     C** SET START OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE COUPON DATE
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDZZLCD     ZSDATE
     C*
     C** SET GREATER THAN LIMITS ON LF/SECED
     C*
     C           ##SEVK    SETGTSECED
     C*
     C** READ FROM LF/SECED
     C*
     C           ##SESN    READESECED                    91
     C*
     C** READ UNTIL THE EVENT HAS AN EVENT TYPE EQUAL TO 'PP' 'MP' OR 'IR'
     C*
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ'0'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'PP'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'MP'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'IR'
     C           ##SESN    READESECED                    91
     C                     END
     C*
     C** SET GREATER THAN LIMITS ON LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           ##BPSK    SETGTBKPOSDF
     C*
     C** READ EQUAL FROM LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           ##BPSP    READEBKPOSDF                  92
     C*
     C** DO WHILE NOT END OF FILE ON LF/SECED
     C** AND NOT END OF FILE ON LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ'0'
     C           *IN92     OREQ '0'
     C*
     C** IF NOT END OF FILE ON LF/SECED
     C*
     C           *IN91     IFEQ '0'
     C*
     C** IF NOT END OF FILE ON LF/BKPOS AND THE EVENT DATE
     C** FROM LF/SECED  IS LESS THAN OR EQUAL TO THE POSITION DATE
     C** FROM LF/BKPOS  OR END OF FILE ON LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           *IN92     IFEQ '0'
     C           SDED      ANDLEBPPD
     C           SDED      ANDLT##IDAT
     C           *IN92     OREQ '1'
     C           SDED      ANDLT##IDAT
     C*
     C** SET THE END OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE EVENT
     C** DATE FROM LF/SECED
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDSDED      ZEDATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZRATE TO GET THE EFFECTIVE
     C** INTEREST RATE FOR THE PERIOD
     C*
     C                     EXSR ZRATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZACCR TO CALCULATE THE INTEREST
     C** FOR THE PERIOD
     C*
     C                     EXSR ZACCR
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL ACCRUED INTEREST
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZACCRD    ##INT
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL NUMBER OF DAYS
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZDDAYS    ##DAYS
     C*
     C** SET THE START OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE
     C** EVENT DATE FROM LF/SECED
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDSDED      ZSDATE
     C*
     C** SET THE FIELDS USED BY ZRATE
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDSDNC      ZCPNR
     C                     Z-ADDSDCP      ZCFCT
     C                     MOVE SDTP      ZPPCP
     C*
     C** READ EQUAL FROM LF/SECED  WITH THE SECURITY SHORTNAME
     C*
     C           ##SESN    READESECED                    91
     C*
     C** READ UNTIL THE EVENT HAS AN EVENT TYPE SDET EQUAL TO 'PP' 'MP' OR 'IR'
     C*
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ'0'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'PP'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'MP'
     C           SDET      ANDNE'IR'
     C           ##SESN    READESECED                    91
     C                     END
     C*
     C** ELSE, IF EVENT DATE FROM LF/SECED  IS GREATER THAN OR
     C** EQUAL TO THE TO DATE PARAMETER, TREAT AS END OF FILE ON LF/SECED
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C           SDED      IFGE ##IDAT
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN91
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C*
     C** IF NOT END OF FILE ON LF/BKPOSDF
     C*
     C           *IN92     IFEQ '0'
     C*
     C** IF NOT END OF FILE ON LF/SECED  AND THE POSITION DATE FROM
     C** LF/BKPOS IS LESS THAN THE EVENT DATE FROM LF/SECED
     C** OR END OF FILE ON LF/SECED
     C*
     C           *IN91     IFEQ '0'
     C           BPPD      ANDLTSDED
     C           BPPD      ANDLT##IDAT
     C           *IN91     OREQ '1'
     C           BPPD      ANDLT##IDAT
     C*
     C** SET THE END OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE
     C** POSITION DATE FROM LF/BKPOSDF
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDBPPD      ZEDATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZRATE TO GET THE EFFECTIVE
     C** INTEREST RATE FOR THE PERIOD
     C*
     C                     EXSR ZRATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZACCR TO CALCULATE THE INTEREST
     C** FOR THE PERIOD
     C                     EXSR ZACCR
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL ACCRUED INTEREST
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZACCRD    ##INT
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL NUMBER OF DAYS
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZDDAYS    ##DAYS
     C*
     C** SET THE START OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE
     C** POSITION DATE FROM LF/BKPOSDF
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDBPPD      ZSDATE
     C*
     C** SET THE NOMINAL
     C*
     C           NPSN      SUB  ECNP      ZAMT
     C*
     C** READ EQUAL FROM LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C           ##BPSP    READEBKPOSDF                  92
     C*
     C** ELSE, IF POSITION DATE FROM LF/BKPOS IS GREATER THAN OR EQUAL
     C** TO THE TO DATE PARAMETER, TREAT AS END OF FILE ON LF/BKPOS
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C           BPPD      IFGE ##IDAT
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN92
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C*
     C** SET THE END OF INTEREST PERIOD DATE EQUAL TO THE TO DATE
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD##IDAT    ZEDATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZRATE TO GET THE EFFECTIVE
     C** INTEREST RATE FOR THE PERIOD
     C*
     C                     EXSR ZRATE
     C*
     C** EXECUTE ZACCR TO CALCULATE THE INTEREST
     C** FOR THE PERIOD
     C*
     C                     EXSR ZACCR
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL ACCRUED INTEREST
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZACCRD    ##INT
     C*
     C** ADD TO THE TOTAL NUMBER OF DAYS
     C*
     C                     ADD  ZDDAYS    ##DAYS
     C*
     C           EINTCA    ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     DUMP
     C                     MOVEL'*ERROR'  ##RETC
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDSR
